title: The Time Tunnel - The Day The Sky Fell In Ep. 4
description: From the west of 1910 the team travels forward to the Japanese Consulate on Hawai'i in 1941 - a day before the Japanese attack that smashes the American Naval Base Pearl Harbor and awakens a sleeping giant. But that's tomorrow's news - today's is Tony's desperate attempt to learn what happened to his father, who disappeared during the attack and was never seen again. And they must evade the murderous efforts of the Japanese agents who are convinced the Americans did not appear in their consulate by mistake.
